asset.hookText: http://www.skis.com/Rossignol-Frenemy-MagTek-Womens-Snowboard-2013/280942,default,pd.html  The Rossignol Frenemy MagTek womens snowboard is an all terrain, all mountain board that is perfect for the any rider. The Frenemy has a directional twin shape with a twin all-mountain flex making it perfect for new riders looking to get out on the slopes. This all mountain board is forgiving enough to help you master the basics. With Magnetraction 5S edges allow for supreme edge hold in any situation by adding 5 more contact points. The sick graphics will ensure that you are the coolest chick on the mountain, while you spin in the park, lay first tracks in the fluff or rip down hard packed the Frenemy MagTek is up for whatever, whenever.
